{"tid":939771,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同唔同女性友人單獨出街食飯好？","createTime":"2018-12-13T11:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T15:15:49.000Z","uid":72186,"like":22,"dislike":113,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5d584c601666ea0ca1a099a965c88c3e4217393a","tid":939771,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:36:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我有個識咗好耐嘅女性友人<br />\n就快出國讀書<br />\n其實一直都feel到佢對我有啲嘢<br />\n但我心入面一直當佢fd所以無點解釋<br />\n最近佢話單獨約我去九龍塘食嘢<br />\n本身我都1516 但見佢又就出國所以咪應承囉<br />\n<br />\n女朋友聽到之後就發晒脾氣 話唔好去<br />\n去咗就係愛滋鴨 唔好返嚟搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢本身毒毒地無咩朋友 我哋都係興趣班識<br />\n但我覺得佢今次好過份<br />\n佢一嬲就咩都講得出 唔理人感受<br />\n而家我同朋友食飯係咪都唔得？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主應該錫返女朋友 唔赴約唔好畀佢擔心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 飛咗條女 依啲女人小氣 同朋友食餐飯都唔得"},{"pid":"0e5dbe8f8a52ae0fcd0c8172ea497ba4b9068c7a","tid":939771,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:37:21.000Z","msg":"y not ?"},{"pid":"d7428aac616d1672ef34eb81cc37f1db3e739d5c","tid":939771,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e5dbe8f8a52ae0fcd0c8172ea497ba4b9068c7a","tid":939771,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:37:21.000Z","msg":"y not ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:39:17.000Z","msg":"y not both <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1106dcf59a859ba5a399899972665b5389e83fea","tid":939771,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7428aac616d1672ef34eb81cc37f1db3e739d5c","tid":939771,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e5dbe8f8a52ae0fcd0c8172ea497ba4b9068c7a","tid":939771,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:37:21.000Z","msg":"y not ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:39:17.000Z","msg":"y 